{"tid":182181,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【考完PHY既DSE雞入】","createTime":"2017-04-01T06:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T12:29:19.000Z","uid":10366,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9bec5b2a2d8c7e9ddb4e2dd7078105d6feecdc37","tid":182181,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:36:08.000Z","msg":"放鬆啦 我考過2013 2014嘅PHY<br />\n年年一考完 d人就話易到仆街 要90%要有5 95%先有星 真係得啖笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本個cut off年年都咁上下<br />\n我自己就次次柒mc既 應該都有人同我一樣啦 mc苦手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要拎星唔一定下下要9成幾既 唔好嚇自己啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地只係想踩低你 擾亂你考其他科既心情 部分人更加唔係考生 只係以為自己讀過下AL就高人一等去踩你拎存在感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n快d溫下一科啦 加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日考既 留言講下今年份卷比起2012-2016 難左定易左 上左岸既就唔好入黎嚇DSE雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb993b23a088293ff77373c9fa00183ece7915a1","tid":182181,"uid":89729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:37:44.000Z","msg":"其實今年易左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb1172745c149158cc322e0fbde61470aa440ea","tid":182181,"uid":10366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實今年易左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁極端既 有冇人今日考架<br />\n<br />\n好多師弟同我講話難左 好想睇下份卷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c1882dbe4f1e3147c00f9d1c72b999e65ac47f8","tid":182181,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T06:40:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實今年易左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd92d5d1c74da39a953d81d1a6369457f807daa4","tid":